item.content:encoded:
Christmas 2023 Update

New Feature found that needs to re-create or re-generate the audio files I advised that if you want higher quality audio do not use it because it because it will degrade the quallity of audio.
In order Anti Synthesizer work, it needs to generate or create the audio again. This doesn't protect the old audio files that has already been distribute.

Version

Target: Phantasium Studio Silicon (P.S.S)

Version: Phantasium Studio Update 1

New

BATCH 1

  • PSAI Rail – Male PSAI
  • PSAI Fenrir – Female PSAI
  • Anti Synthesizer – 
  • Server Base Requirements – In order to save space on our machine, Phantasium Studio Silicon will download PSAI, Models, or any requirement in our server.  The users have an option to save the contents downloaded or re-download it once it needs again this will save alot of disk space since Phantasium Studio Silicon takes alot of disk space.
  • Server Base Backup – Phantasium Studio Silicon now be backup in one push of a button. Rather than having a portable copy of Phantasium Studio Silicon. Portable Copy takes long to process, and it takes a lot of disk space. This update, reduce it by saving a stable version itself on our server. Can be restored by downloading your backup from our server.
Batch 2
  • Anti Synthesizer (Partially Implemented) – This reduce the chances the voices generated or created in Phantasium Studio Silicon being cloned by 3rd party software or AI.

Bug Fixed

BATCH 1

  • PSAI Luette – Mimic Emotion Fixed

Christmas 2023 Update

Version

Target: Hinachi Ai (HAi)

Version: Hinachi Ai 3.0.2312

New

BATCH 1

  • Pose Editor – Hinachi Ai can now illustrate a specific pose with or without a reference. By openning Pose Editor, you can customized, give reference, or create a pose you want.
  • Server Base Requirements – In order to save space on our machine, Hinachi Ai will download diffusers, renderers, or any requirement in our server.  The users can has an option to save the contents downloaded or re-download it once it needs again this will save alot of disk space since Hinachi Ai takes alot of disk space.
  • Server Base Backup – Hinachi Ai now be backup in one push of a button. Rather than having a portable copy of Hinachi Ai. Portable Copy takes long to process and it takes alot of disk space. This update, reduce it by saving a stable version itself on our server. Can be restored by downloading your backup from our server.
  • Added Lora Support

Improved

BATCH 1

  • Illustration Speed has been Improved

item.title: Hinachi Ai
item.dc:creator: Xeno
item.description: Hinachi Ai is an advanced AI Illustrator created by Xeno Gen Projects that primarily targets the “Toon-Anime'' art style.
item.content:encoded:
Hinachi Ai Access Changed October 14, 2023 Hinachi Ai can no longer be accesable to public.

What is Hinachi Ai?

Hinachi Ai is an advanced AI Illustrator created by Xeno Gen Projects that primarily target for “Toon-Anime” art style. Even tho, its primarily build for “Toon-Anime” art style. It’s not limited, Hinachi Ai can also produce realistic art style.

Hinachi Ai was public available in November 3, 2022 but on October 14, 2023 it become a private tool for Xeno Gen Projects due to inefficient budget to maintain for public use.

View More
Twitter

Diffusers and Renderers

Hinachi Ai uses combination between diffuser and renderer in order to illustrate an image.

Diffusers

Features

AI Correction

We noticed AI Corrections perform is well dependent on art style.

AI Corrections try to correct “what’s wrong” or “out of place” from the image output. This doesn’t correct all but reduced the number of errors within an image output.

Censorship

Hinachi Ai can produce image between SFW and NSFW.

Composition Prompt

Not yet Documented

Emphasizer

Not yet Documented

Image Allusion

This feature is able us to use image as reference and Hinachi Ai will make an idea out of it.

AI Precision Vector

This will help AI Correction to perform more.

Betterness Focal Point (BFP)

Better Focal Point is a technique that adds more quality of the image by simulating virtual rays.

Color Enhancement

Image shows the effect of Color Enhancement 1.1

This feature mimics the aura of Anime Style for the image output.

Renderer Optimized

It optimized the renderer by lessening the GPU Usage and the image quality and in exchange of huge performance increase.

 

It does reduce image quality, but it almost has small difference, and the difference aren’t noticeable when compared to the un-optimized version.
